metadata.name: 「Fine Dining 101」
metadata.description:
𝐅𝐢𝐧𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟏
You're teaching Merry Meritt the dinner date etiquette. The way she used the utensils are rather peculiar, as if she has a different idea - however, it's a start. She takes note of your every word.

「 So, like, you don't use knives only for stabbing?」
「...yes, you don't.」
